nodes.text: Dxulininan was the author of a book entitled Warm Thoughts for Invertebrates. On the date 13:2:28, according to HoloNet News, Dxulininan's book was number-three on a list of best-sellers.

A ranking of the five best-selling books, from 23 BBY, including the number-three ranked Warm Thoughts for Invertebrates, appeared in HoloNet News Vol. 531 45 (2002), an in-universe website created to publicize the upcoming Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones film. Dxulininan was credited for the book in its entry on this list. Pablo Hidalgo and Paul Ens wrote the site content.
